# Keep the build context tiny: only pyproject/uv.lock, src/, config/, README.md
# are COPYed by the Dockerfile. Everything else — especially the multi-GB host
# .venv, .git, and the compose volume dirs — must never ship to the daemon.
.venv/
.git/
.claude/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
qdrant_storage/
ollama_data/
redis_data/
data/
docs/
tests/
scripts/
.env
*.md
!README.md
